** INSTALANDO BOOTSTRAP **
 -> http://v4-alpha.getbootstrap.com/getting-started/download/#package-managers
 -> https://ng-bootstrap.github.io/#/getting-started
$ npm install --save bootstrap@4.0.0-alpha.6 font-awesome
  Depois do comando acima, ajustar o angular-cli.json inserindo o seguinte codigo:
  "styles": [
    "../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css",
    "../node_modules/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css",
    "styles.css"
  ],
  "scripts": [
    "../node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.js",
    "../node_modules/tether/dist/js/tether.js",
    "../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.js"
  ]

http://v4-alpha.getbootstrap.com/

