** UTILIZANDO MATERIAL DESIGN FOR ANGULAR 2 **
> Instalando <https://github.com/angular/material2/blob/master/guides/getting-started.md>
> Docs <https://material.angular.io/components/component/input>
> Icones <https://material.io/icons/> <http://google.github.io/material-design-icons/#icon-font-for-the-web>


** SOBRE ANGULAR 2 **
Make sure to add "FormsModule" to your "AppModule" for the Template-Driven approach and "ReactiveFormsModule" in your
"AppModule" for the Data-Driven approach.
